<Alloy>
	<View id="index" class="container">
		<View id="dashboard" formFactor="handheld">
			<ScrollView id="now">
				<Label id="lblHome" text="ticonf.eu is a new mobile development conference primarily based around JavaScript and Appcelerator Titanium. It's a 2-day, not-for-profit, community run event featuring some of the best JavaScript and Titanium Mobile developers from Europe and the UK. The event is to take place between the 23rd-24th of February 2013 - entry and tickets are open to all regardless of your skill level! We welcome beginners and experts alike."></Label>
